---
title: Smokey Mild Chorizo & Bean Chilli with Cheddar Cheese & Rice
description: Oops, we've done it again – put a clever twist on a weekday favourite to bring you something new and exciting, with flavours we know you love! Our latest chilli creation is a mix of chorizo, red kidney beans, corn and Cheddar cheese with the irresistible flavour of our All-American spice blend.
